node.text:
Today is publication day! I am so excited to finally share my life and this book with you. This book is for everyone to read! There are still so many ways to get the book! 

You can click the link in my bio, download the @nate_app and follow my summer list.

If you are in NYC, you can swipe up on my stories and join us tonight at 6:30pm ET at @strandbookstore to get a signed copy!

Make sure you go get a copy and come join us today!

*GIVEAWAY* If you know me, you know I love me some Shake Shack and the simplicity of Grubhub! So me and @mattjames919 are teaming up with @shakeshack and @grubhub to hook you up with the ultimate summer spread - Shake Shack’s new summer menu! And now through Aug 1st, we got you covered with a BOGO on their Summerades plus free delivery on your Grubhub order of $15+. 

For my NYC fam, tag a friend below, tell us which NYC neighborhood you live in and follow @grubhub  + @shakeshack  for a chance to win a personal delivery from me and Matt. If you live outside NYC, just tag a friend for a chance to win a personal shoutout video + Grubhub gift card. Winners will be chosen by midnight tomorrow! 

Terms Apply: grhb.me/ShakeShackGiveaway
